_sText:
ze_santa_prison_escape
ver : final_fix

// information 

- map made in 2 weeks for Christmas Nide 2024

- this map is made for zombie escape mode 

- map made according to the game Escape Barry Prison Run in Roblox

- Materials and models from ze_christmas_beta / christmas_infection / ze_santassination

// Map info : 

- some parts have to separate teams to help pave the way for each other

- map time: ~ 15 minutes 

- map has 3 human items : heal / fire / toxic

- 1 santa boss 

- train ending 

- traps

- HDR for better quality 

- thank you to those who played the test and those who gave suggestions to make the map more complete - dear
